		<div class="comment_entry">
			<p>Similar trick with boiled potatoes:<br />
1) Before cooking perform two large crossed incisions on the skin.<br />
2) Cook the potatoes in boiling water<br />
3) Put the potatoes into icy water<br />
4) The skin just &#8220;slips&#8221; out when you press it sligthly.</p>
