			<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/blog/2008/07/02/how-to-peel-hard-boiled-eggs-without-peeling/?replytocom=23126#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-23126", "23126", "respond", "378")'>Reply</a>	</div>
