			<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/a08a9a5ae8d1009eebe518998990d7f6?s=64&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=R' class='avatar avatar-64 photo' height='64' width='64' />		</div>
		<div class="comment_entry">
			<p>A word to the wise, make sure your egg isn&#8217;t too soft boiled before you try this!</p>
<p>One more diet hack: 2 steps to never having an &#8216;off plan&#8217; work meal again</p>
<p>1) The Pret Audit:<br />
Have a look round the eateries where you work, compile a list of at least 10 dishes that conform to the diet you need an keep it in your desk. Select 2 dishes from the list before you go out and buy one.<br />
2) The Double Dinner<br />
Just cook 2x the amount of dinner you need and take it to work the next day. Prepare twice as much protein and vegetables as you need, divide or apportion carbs as needed (exercise, goals etc)</p>
<p>More &#8216;hacks&#8217; at my blog (click my name)</p>
