			</span>
			<br />
			<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/8e2569ebeda301d241bb9e4aff4c633d?s=64&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=R' class='avatar avatar-64 photo' height='64' width='64' />		</div>
		<div class="comment_entry">
			<p>Hiya &#8230;<br />
Just got to see this vid.  Neat trick &#8230; will try it tomorrow when I do my usual eggy breakfast.<br />
BUT<br />
Just have to let y&#8217;all know that the fresher the egg, the more difficult it is to peel.  Good way of telling how old your supermarket eggs REALLY are, albeit a bit late!  So if you&#8217;ve got wonderfully fresh eggs, forget hard boiling them.  Soft boil, poach or make an omelette.<br />
Bon Appetit!</p>
