			<p>There are a ton of great cooking and food hacks on <a href="http://www.chowhound.com" rel="nofollow">http://www.chowhound.com</a> &#8212; they&#8217;re short videos called Chow tips. My favorite is how to store strawberries (my favorite food) &#8212; you place two damp towels around the strawberries, above and below, with the strawberries placed in one layer between the towels, not all piled up on to of one another. It is amazing how long the strawberries stay fresh that way.</p>
